comment: Without evidence, President Trump accused the chairman of the House Intelligence Committee of leaking information about Russias effort to interfere in the 2020 election https://t.co/ES16HpuWz5

The biggest threat to our elections is a president who welcomes foreign help.But the biggest danger to our democracy is a president who liesconstantly.I dont discuss classified briefings, but you dont need a clearance to see how Trump endangers everything we hold dear.
